observe.desc:
[
{"Whale Explosion" is a rare natural phenomenon that typically occurs when a whale strands or dies. The combination of external air pressure and internal gas generated by decomposition causes the body to burst, creating a sudden explosion of flesh, blood, and organs.}
]

      [
      {<Excerpted data from an encyclopedia>
Whenever a person dies and the body is not embalmed within 5 to 8 days, it undergoes a high degree of decay. This process produces a large amount of putrid gases which fill the soft tissues throughout the body, resulting in severe swelling including an extremely swollen face and protruding eyeballs, thickened and turned out lips, stretched out tongue, abdominal expansion, green skin, subcutaneous tissue and muscle emphysema, thickening of the limbs, the entire body swollen into a giant, it becomes difficult to guess how it used to look in life, this phenomenon is known as the Liquefactive stage of decomposition.}
      ]

      [
      {Several children were taken from their homes by an unknown man.
Their parents begged us to find them offering a generous reward, and our staff eventually discovered them in a contaminated pool at an industrial site. Most of the children were badly affected by radiation, and a few were confirmed dead. Not far from where the children were, we found many decomposing bodies in Liquefactive state. with a strange man.
Later, an investigation revealed that the man suffered from intense paranoia. He used his description of the ocean to lure some children, who had never been exposed to the ocean, to a waste pool.
We do not know what the parents of those children did to him. However, we found his body one week later.}
